        public void multiply()

      • divide

        public void divide()
        Divides two complex numbers. (a + bi) / (x + yi) = ((a + bi) * (x - yi)) / (xx + yy) Example (2 + 5i) / (3 + i) = (11/10 + 13/10i) = (1.1 + 1.3i)
